__Learn, Compare, Practice__

- Read _Steering the Craft_ along side _Five Ways to Forgiveness_ using the following pattern: after 2 chapters of SC, read one of the stories in FWF. Look for examples of what was introduced in SC within the stories. Keep notes.
- Complete the assignments within SC.

__Refine__

- Read the essay/story combo by Le Guin in _Those Who Can_ by Robin Scott Wilson.
- Write a flash fiction story emulating something from the story.

